Magneto is on a one-man mission to safeguard the future of mutantkind by any means necessary. So far, he&#39;s done so by eliminating human threats&hellip;
But what happens when it&#39;s MUTANTS who pose a threat to their own species?
Will Magneto cross a line and raise his hand to his own kind? And if so, just how far will he go?

